overview:
Seven Playgrounds is a photography company.

Wedding Photography is the our specialty. The process starts from the beginning of Engagement Photos, and Bridal photography. The day of the wedding Seven Playgrounds is usually the first on the scene and the last to leave capturing all of the most important moments. Then down the road they are also available for family photos once your family begins to grow.

Seven Playgrounds is a one stop shot for all of your photographic needs.
